title: Everyone should want to share a knowledge graph.
pid: 61eb92ea-276a-4479-81aa-d509731f76cf
body: |2-
  We must improve human nature before we destroy ourselves. Every adult has an obligation to continue studying the things we tell children we understand: love, justice, art, death, honor, peace, desire, all the high ideas.

  But the universe of things to study is big. We can't do it well without helping each other. Privacy and sharing; reading, writing and thinking; we need to process information faster, better, by reducing the friction between these things. A shared knowledge graph can do that.
